[[File:Dockyard Museum.jpg|thumbnail|350px|Dockyard Museum at [[Nelson's Dockyard]] on [[Antigua]] island.]] The '''Dockyard Museum''' is a [[museum]] located at [[Nelson's Dockyard]] in [[English Harbour]] on [[Antigua]] island, in [[Antigua and Barbuda]].
It was established in 1855 at the colonial British shipyard.<ref>[http://www.antiguanice.com/v2/client.php?id=111&cat=13 The Dockyard Museum] ( {{webarchive|url=https://www.webcitation.org/64XgthOim?url=http://www.antiguanice.com/v2/client.php?id=111&cat=13 |date=8 January 2012 }})</ref>
