{{Orphan|date=October 2014}} {{Infobox comedian | name = Gennady Vetrov | image = Геннадий Ветров в Архангельске (6).JPG | imagesize = | caption = | pseudonym = | birth_name = Gennady Vetrov | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1958|11|18}} | birth_place = [[Makiivka]], [[Soviet Union]] | death_date = | death_place = | medium = | nationality = | active = | genre = Satire | subject = | influences = | influenced = | spouse = | domesticpartner = | notable_work = | signature = | website = http://vetrov-show.ru/ | footnotes = | current_members = | past_members = }}
'''Gennady Anatolyevich Vetrov''' ({{lang-ru|Генна́дий Анато́льевич Ве́тров}}; born November 18, 1958 in Makiyivka, Donetsk region) is a Soviet and Russian satirist and humorist, singer, Honored Artist of Russia (August 9, 2009).<ref name="1062-1995">[http://graph.document.kremlin.ru/page.aspx?1022804 УКАЗ Президента РФ от 09.08.2009 N 924]</ref><ref>[http://beliylebed34.ru/programs/arkhiv_programmy_klassika_yumora/artisty-yumoristy/361/ Ветров Геннадий Анатольевич]</ref>
== Biography== Gennady Vetrov was born on November 18, 1958, in Makiyivka (Donetsk region) in the family of a former coal miner who became a hairdresser.<ref>[http://www.vetrov-show.ru/p10.html#p10 Артист и юморист Геннадий Ветров. Биография, песни, видео, официальный сайт Ветрова]</ref> He has graduated from [[Makiivka Civil Engineering Institute]].
In 1988 he graduated from the acting and directing course in [[Russian State Institute of Performing Arts|LGITMiK]]. He has worked in the theater "Buff", toured the United States, Switzerland, Germany and France. Worked for several years in Germany. In 1992 he gave 33 recitals in the United States. Member of television programs "Shire Krug", "Full House", "Piano in the bush", "Fun". Gennady Vetrov lead television programs "Piano in the bush", "Shire Krug", "Funny People".<ref>[http://donbass.name/159-vetrov-gennadijj-anatolevich.html Ветров Геннадий Анатольевич]</ref>
The founder and leader of the pop group "Vetrov's people" (in Russian it sounds like "Windy people").<ref>[http://www.umoristy.ru/p18.html Геннадий Ветров, интервью для Юмористы.ру]</ref>
=== Personal life === *First wife - businesswoman Anastasia Smolina (involved in the organization of holidays).<ref>[http://neformat.co.ua/index.php?nma=news&fla=stat&nums=13395 Почему распался брак Геннадия Ветрова| Геннадий ветров — Неформат. Информационный портал<!-- Заголовок добавлен ботом -->]</ref> ** A daughter - actress Ksenia Vetrova (born August 5, 1993).<ref name="celebirthday.narod.ru">[http://celebirthday.narod.ru/startv2.htm День рожденья звёзд]</ref><ref>[http://www.freshfilms.su/actors-base/kseniya-vetrova Ксения Ветрова - Актерское агентство Freshfilms<!-- Заголовок добавлен ботом -->]</ref><ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LzZd64gXL38 Ксения Ветрова в программе "Пока все дома" - YouTube<!-- Заголовок добавлен ботом -->]</ref><ref>[http://glavr.ru/index/vetrova_ksenija/0-547 Актёрское агентство «Главная роль» - Ветрова Ксения<!-- Заголовок добавлен ботом -->]</ref><ref>[http://www.telesem.ru/teleheroes/527 Геннадий Ветров: Шарон Стоун меня уже достала<!-- Заголовок добавлен ботом -->]</ref> * Second wife - actress Karina Zvereva (to 2011).<ref name=autogenerated1>[http://star-town.ru/life/1-rus/1329-vetrov-zvereva.html Юморист Геннадий Ветров и Карина Зверева развелись<!-- Заголовок добавлен ботом -->]</ref><ref>[http://www.beer7.net/2011/08/blog-post_11.html Программа «Ветреные люди» в Израиле]</ref> * Third wife - stewardess Oksana Voronicheva from Arkhangelsk.<ref>[http://www.pravdasevera.ru/newspaper/2014/79/personal_life/gennadij-vetrov-ya-zhenilsya-na-devushke-iz-arhangelska/ Геннадий Ветров: Я женился на девушке из Архангельска]</ref> ** A daughter - Mary Vetrov (1 June 2016).
