'''La 1/2 Docena''' is a [[Costa Rica]]n [[comedy]] group formed by Mario Chacon, Erik Hernández, Edgar Murillo, and Daniel Moreno.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nacion.com/2010-07-29/Entretenimiento/NotasSecundarias/Entretenimiento2462573.aspx |title=La 1/2 Docena desempolvará recuerdos en su sexta temporada |last=Flores |first=Yancy Ana M. |date=29 July 2010 |work=La Nación |language=Spanish |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/62Mh1mXmJ?url=http://www.nacion.com/2010-07-29/Entretenimiento/NotasSecundarias/Entretenimiento2462573.aspx |archivedate=11 October 2011 |deadurl=yes |df= }}</ref> Two of their projects are ''El Show de La 1/2 Docena'' and ''La 1/2 Docena en el Teatro''.

