{{Use dmy dates|date=March 2018}} {{Infobox company | name = SnapDragon Games GmbH | logo = | type = [[Privately held company|Private]] | industry = [[Video game industry]] | fate = [[Insolvency]] | founded = {{Start date and age|df=yes|2005|10|13}} | founder = Christian von Duisburg | defunct = {{End date|2010}} | hq_location_city = [[Hamburg]] | hq_location_country = [[Germany]] | key_people = Christian von Duisburg {{small|([[Chief executive officer|CEO]])}} | num_employees = 5<ref>https://www.bild.de/spiele/archiv/wickie-snapdragon-9535542.bild.html</ref> | num_employees_year = 2009 }}
'''SnapDragon Games GmbH''' was a German [[video game developer]] based in [[Hamburg]]. The company was founded by Christian von Duisburg in October 2005. Following the demise of [[CDV Software]], SnapDragon Games filed for [[insolvency]] in 2010.<ref>http://www.eurogamer.de/articles/the-kore-gang-vorschau_3</ref>
