'''''The Voice Weekly''''' was a news journal published in [[Burmese language]]. It was more focused on Burmese political issues. It was suspended one week together with ''[[Seven Days News|7 Days News]]'' for publishing [[Aung San Suu Kyi]] news on front page in November 2011.<ref>[http://digitaljournal.com/article/300576 Myanmar suspends nine news journals for Suu Kyi coverage<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref> The magazine was suspended by the government in July 2012.<ref>{{cite news|title=Two Burmese Journals Suspended|url=http://www.rfa.org/english/news/myanmar/media-07312012193931.html|accessdate=13 April 2016|work=Radio Free Asia|date=31 July 2012}}</ref>
